3):&nbsp;<a href=\"http://203.129.234.86/husim/hotcrp/scorehelp.php?f=interestToCommunity\">(?)</a></p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">4.&nbsp;Good</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">A8. Outreach (Items 14, 16, 17):&nbsp;<a href=\"http://203.129.234.86/husim/hotcrp/scorehelp.php?f=longevity\">(?)</a></p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">3.&nbsp;Bordering Acceptable</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">A9. Please provide your comments and suggestions for improvement on Items A1-A8 in 8 succeeding paragraphs, numbered paragraphs.</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Item 7 &amp; 8 are not clearly stated. How the validation will be done ? What are the bench mark with which they will compare the product developed &amp; its applicability ?</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B1. Any major mismatches in the proposed line item costs with the proposed item/work, in the format: Budget-head-Institution: Remarks. Example: &lt;Manpower-IITX: Remarks&gt;</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Workshop Fund : Such a costly system development must be disseminated regularly via training of researcher/application personnel, should not be limited to IISc/IIT&#39;s only, otherwise developed machinery will be useless and will remain theoretical without actual implimentation. Suggestion is : last year conducting workshops (at least twice a year) with researchers/doctors/health related personnel etc.is appropriate evaluation method and will significantly improve the user based utility of such system.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B2. Any major equipment proposed for purchase that may be otherwise possible to share with others or is usable through outsourcing, without adversely affecting the work.</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">HW budget : Needs to be justified why can not be shared with existing facilities in IISC .</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C2. Your Overall Evaluation:&nbsp;<a href=\"http://203.129.234.86/husim/hotcrp/scorehelp.php?f=grammar\">(?)</a>(shown only to chairs)</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">A.&nbsp;Recommended for Support</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">MIsc&nbsp;Text(shown only to chairs)</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Evaluation from HW experts for the mentioned purchase/development of such Multi-FPGA Based Accelerated/Prototyping System &ldquo;Morphing Machines&rdquo;, must be considered.</p>\r\n', '', '1'),
