ly in India) where its sharing/outsourcing may be possible, and (ii) is it absolutely necessary for the project.</p>\n\n<hr />\n<p>-</p>\n\n<p>C1. Any Additional Comments:</p>\n\n<hr />\n<p>International relevance of the study should be made a compulsory sub heading along with the proposed publication timeline.</p>\n\n<p>C2. Your Overall Evaluation:&nbsp;<a href=\"http://203.129.234.86/husim/hotcrp/scorehelp.php?f=grammar\">(?)</a>(shown only to chairs)</p>\n\n<hr />\n<p>C.&nbsp;Not Recommended for Support</p>\n\n<h4><font color=\"#008000\"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></font></h4>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n', '', '1');
