itle: <strong>Cognitive computing</strong> &ndash;Refresher course on computer science and&nbsp; Information Technology, University of Kerala</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Year February 2018</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Participants:40</p>\r\n', '<p>1. Title: <strong>Discussions were held with the Indian Navy about the prospective LR Wi-Fi communication system</strong><br />\r\nYear: 2014<br />\r\n<br />\r\n2.Title: <strong>Poster sessions on MICRONET was held during RT Labs national level workshop funded by MHRD</strong><br />\r\nYear: 2015<br />\r\n<br />\r\n3. Title: <strong>Poster sessions on MICRONET was held during HFSS design workshop.</strong><br />\r\nYear: 2015<br />\r\n<br />\r\n4. Title: <strong>Poster sessions on MICRONET was held during Final Year M.Tech Wireless Networks &amp;Applications project reviews, conducted by Amrita University in order to create awareness among visitors and participants of the events.</strong><br />\r\nYear: 2015<br />\r\n<br />\r\n5. Title: <strong>Micronet work was show cased during the one day international conference on &#39;Technology for Sustainable Development&#39; conducted by United Nations Academic Impact &amp; Amrita University at New York</strong><br />\r\nYear: 2015<br />\r\n<br />\r\n6. Title: <strong>As a part of Amrita University Chancellor Amma&#39;s 62nd birthday celebrations, the project was exhibited to the public to instill awareness on the application of Science &amp; Technology for Fisherman community.</strong><br />\r\nYear: 2015</p>\r\n\r\n<p>7. Title: <strong>Brief presentation of MICRONet project to the Minister of Fisheries Mercy Kutty Amma, Director of Fisheries and other Govt. officials and Industrial stake holders by Dr.Elizabeth Sherly and team.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Year: January 2017</p>\r\n\r\n<p>8. Title: <strong>MICRONet project presentation to Dr.Gulati, Zonal Director Fishery Survey of India (FSI) and other staff members.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Year: November 2017</p>\r\n\r\n<p>9. Title: <strong>Open House </strong>w