(13, '<p style=\"margin-left:.25in\">1. Title: Introduced an elective course at SUIIT</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:.25in\">Insert link to course/module content, or name of attached course/module content file:&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:.25in\">Avg. enrolment per offering: B.Tech-8+7+6+8 (29)</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:.25in\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; M. Tech student-13+13+10+4 (40)</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:.25in\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; M. Sc. 22+19+18+9 (68) (data for four years 2015-2018)</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:.25in\">2. Title: Elective course on &ldquo;Wireless Sensor Network&rdquo; is introduced</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:.25in\">The link to the course module is <a href=\"http://dcis.uohyd.ac.in/Academic/Courses/index.php\">http://dcis.uohyd.ac.in/Academic/Courses/index.php</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:.25in\">Average enrolment per offering:&nbsp; 30 (M. Tech level Students)</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:.25in\">3. Title: Water resources Engineering, Design of hydraulic structures</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:.25in\">Course offered at IIIT, Hyderabad</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:.25in\">4. Title: Elective course &ldquo;Mathematical Modelling of Environment&rdquo; at Department of Mathematics,</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:.25in\">Sambalpur University</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:.25in\">Msc-20+22+12 ( Data for 3 years, 2016-18)</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:.25in\">Mathematical modeling offered at Dept. of mathematics as an elective after the project started. Now a course in</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:.25in\">Mathematical modeling is introduced at BSc level under course credit system. It is approved by Board of studies of</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:.25in\">University and Academic council.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:.25in\">5. Title: New module &ldquo;water pollution&rdquo; is introduced in M.Sc. Environmental Science at Sambalpur University</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:.25in\">6. Title: New module on &ldquo;Application of Sensor Network for Environmental Monitoring: is introduced in the Sensors and Embedded Systems&quot;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:.25in\">The link to the course module is <a href=\"http://dcis.uohyd.ac.in/Academic/Courses/index.php\">http://dcis.uohyd.ac.in/Academic/Courses/index.php</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Average enrolment per offering:&nbsp; 20 (M. Tech level Students)</p>\r\n', '<p><strong>AquaSense Lab</strong> project Labs have been set-up at UoH, VNRVJIET, SUIIT</p>\r\n\r\n<p>These Labs are set-up with the grant received from this project and exclusively used by the project staff and students working in this project.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1. Name of the Lab: ITRA-AquaSense Lab</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Center for Modelling, Simulation and Design (CMSD), University of Hyderabad</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2. Name of the Lab: AquaSense</p>\r\n\r\n<p>First Floor, Sambalpur University Institute for Information Technology Sambalpur University, Sambalpur (Orissa)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3. Name of the Lab: WSN-Lab</p>\r\n\r\n<p>VNRVJIET, Bachupally, Hyderabad</p>\r\n\r\n<p>4. Lab: Introduced a Lab component in the course in association with Quadratyx Technologies (Hyderabad), Lab established at IIIT, Hyderabad&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>5. Lab: Fluid mechanics lab</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Lab established at IIIT, Hyderabad:&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>6. Lab: Simulation Lab</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Lab Established at IIIT, Hyderabad</p>\r\n\r\n<p>7.Name of the Lab: <em>ITRA-Water</em>-AquaSense IOT- Hardware lab, SCCE, Karimnagar</p>\r\n\r\n<p>8. <em>ITRA-Water</em>-AquaSense Software&rsquo;s are established in computer lab, SCIT, Karimnagar</p>\r\n', '<p>1. Title: Updated an elective course on Wireless Sensor Network at UoH</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The link to the course module is <a href=\"http://dcis.uohyd.ac.in/Academic/Courses/index.php\">http://dcis.uohyd.ac.in/Academic/Courses/index.php</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Average enrolment per offering:&nbsp; 30 (M. Tech level Students)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2.Title: Added few modules in the existing &quot;Wireless Sensor Network&rdquo; Course and &ldquo;Embedded Systems&quot; course with hands on at UoH</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The link to the course module is <a href=\"http://dcis.uohyd.ac.in/Academic/Courses/index.php\">http://dcis.uohyd.ac.in/Academic/Courses/index.php</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Average enrolment per offering:&nbsp; 20 (M. Tech level Students)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3. Title:&nbsp; Developed application module Internet of Things</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The link to the course module is <a href=\"http://dcis.uohyd.ac.in/Academic/Courses/index.php\">http://dcis.uohyd.ac.in/Academic/Courses/index.php</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Average enrolment per offering:&nbsp; 15 (M. Tech/ MCA level Students)</p>\r\n', '<p>1. Previously there was no Lab component in the wireless sensor network course and the credit was also 3. Now, we have introduced Lab component and set up a separate lab (Wireless sensor network Lab) and introduced Lab/ practical component based on the learning from the project.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The different research Lab links can be found at <a href=\"http://dcis.uohyd.ac.in/Research/Areas/researchareas.php\">http://dcis.uohyd.ac.in/Research/Areas/researchareas.php</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>2 Lab: 10 node network Test bed was established in fluid mechanics Lab by SCCE, Karimnagar</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3. Embedded Systems Lab at University of Hyderabad</p>\r\n', '<p>The team has initiated a company formation process namely ShunyaInnovations (<a href=\"http://www.shunyainnovations.com\">www.shunyainnovations.com</a>) and also registered a web site. They have not yet done the formal company registration and other formalities.</p>\r\n', '<p>1. Title: Integrated and Intelligent handheld device for water body profiling and monitoring</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Application Number: Submitted to University of Hyderabad Patent Cell and it is under active consideration</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Submission Date (Resubmitted): February 2018</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2. Title: Water level monitoring and early warning system (In Process)</p>\r\n', '<p>0</p>\r\n', '<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"width:708px\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"height:83px; width:708px\">\r\n			<p>1. Title: Wireless Communication: Issues and Challenges</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>Date : 12-13 May 2015</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>Participants: 25</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>2. Title: Sensors and Interfaces</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>Date: 08-12 June 2016</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>Participants: 30</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>3. Title: Radar Communication and its application</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>Date: 27-29 September 2015</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>Participant: 55</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>4. Sensor Network Application</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>Date: 1-3 May 2015</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>Participants: 45</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>5. Title: Machine Learning and Sensor Network</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>Date: 11-12 February 2015</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>Participants: 30</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>6. Title: Big Data Analytics and Applications</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>Date: 11-14 December 2014</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>Participant: 50</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '<p>1. Title: A seminar talk at ANITS, Vishakhapatnam by Prof. Siba K Udgata</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Date : 07-05-2016</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Participants: 60 (Approx.)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2. Title: A Tutorial talk at Berhampur University by Prof. Siba K Udgata</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Date: 06<sup>th</sup> February 2015</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Participants: 100</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3. Title: A Seminar Talk at Kalam Institute of Technology by Dr. S. L .Sabat</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Date: 07<sup>th</sup> December 2016</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Participants: 50</p>\r\n\r\n<p>4. Title: Delivered an Invited Talk at&nbsp; Golden Jubilee Convention at College of Engineering and Technology, OUAT, Bhubaneswar</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Date: 16<sup>th</sup> June 2016</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Participants: 150</p>\r\n\r\n<p>5. Title: Sensor Network and Environment Monitoring at GITAM University, Vishakhapatnam</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Date: 5<sup>th</sup> March 2018</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Participants: 200</p>\r\n', '<p>0</p>\r\n', '<p>1. Title: &quot;Mathematical Modeling of Water Pollution&rdquo; at SUIIT. Many participants from Environmental sciences, Industry and other institutions attended at the workshop.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Date: 14-16<sup>th</sup> February 2015</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Participants: 51 excluding speakers who were from Shanti Niketan, IIT Bhubaneswar, HCU Hyderabad, VSSUT, Software industries, and Sambalpur university</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2. Title: National workshop on simulation using MATLAB at SUIIT</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Date: 5-10<sup>th</sup> March 2016</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Participants: Participant: 25+ Resource persons 6 Nos (From VSSUT, NIT Rourkela, Silicon Institute etc.)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3. One day work shop on Data Analytics for handling water pollution Data on 13<sup>th</sup> December 2015 Speakers were Prof Arun K Pujari, Prof S K Udgata, Dr R Gartia and Dr Hemendra Behera from Pollution control Board, Mr Jethu Bhoi</p>\r\n\r\n<p>4. Title: Workshop on IOT Concepts &ndash; SCCE</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Date: 19-24<sup>th</sup> Sep, 2016</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Participants: 61</p>\r\n\r\n<p>5. Title: Workshop on Cloud Computing &ndash; SCIT</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Date: 03-08<sup>th</sup> Oct, 2016</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Participants: 62</p>\r\n\r\n<p>There are many more Seminars held in IIIT, Hyderabad and some are in collaboration with CMSD, CASEST, and SCIS at University of Hyderabad which are not exclusively not mentioned in this list.</p>\r\n', '<p>1. Title: Open Exhibition for School Children</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Year: Interacted with Batemura school with Mr Ranjan Panda (a water activist) and Prof A. Mishra (an Environment specialist).</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2. Title: Open Session for Villagers</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Year:&nbsp; November 2015</p>\r\n\r\n<p>At Remta village of Baragarh district and Batemura of Sambalpur district</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3. Open Session at two Engineering Colleges SCCE &amp; SCIT</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Year : 2016</p>\r\n', '<p>1. Industry: RAYA Renewable Energy Solutions Pvt. Ltd.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Collaboration Area: Smart Water Meter Mfg &amp; Marketing</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2. Industry:&nbsp; <strong>New Zen Infotech </strong>Pvt. Ltd.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Collaboration Area: Software Application Development</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3. Industry; COIGN CONSULTANTS PVT. LTD.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Collaboration Area: Database Development, Software Application Development</p>\r\n\r\n<p>4. Industry: Light Motif, Hyderabad</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Collaboration Area: Optical Electronics</p>\r\n\r\n<p>5. Industry: MICHRO Ltd, Hyderabad</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Collaboration area: PCB design and Communication</p>\r\n\r\n<p>6. Industry: METRONIX Hyderabad</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Collaboration Area: Code Embedding and STM Microcontroller based product design</p>\r\n', '<p>1. Deptt/Ministry: Collaboration with NIST, Berhampur, Odisha to be part of the smart village at Anugul, Odisha</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Collaboration Area: To field test the prototype</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2. Deptt/Ministry: Collaboration with Water Commission for sharing the Mahanadi River data</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Collaboration Area:&nbsp; We met The Executive Engineer and SDO of Central water commission and invited them for team interactions and requested them for data at their level.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3. Deptt/Ministry: Four village level awareness programmes are conducted at Village Remta and Batemura, Sambalpur, Odisha</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Collaboration Area:&nbsp; Those areas have severe polluted water. We conducted the camps and promised them to help them out which could not be done as no fund has been released for SUIIT since two years.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>4. Deptt/Ministry: Collaboration with Karimnagar Municipal Water Supply for Deployment of the proposed model as a pilot project for one of the Zones. A presentation to Karim Nagar Municipality Corporation Water Board (attended by more than 100 employees)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Collaboration Area: To get the support from the municipality corporation for helping to test the smart meter</p>\r\n\r\n<p>5. Deptt/Ministry: Study of Existing Network in Karimnagar in Rampoor Zone</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Collaboration Area: Support for installation and testing</p>\r\n', '<p>1. NGO: Practical Action</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Collaboration Area: This NGO works at the village level and mainly involved in ensuring improvement in quality of life. We have been collaborating them to</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2. NGO: OXFAM India, Kolkata</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Collaboration Area: This NGO is working on water management issues on Trans-Boundary Rivers of South-Asia (TROSA). We are collaborating on Safe water management issues</p>\r\n', '<p>0</p>\r\n', '<p>1. Organization: Collaboration with School of Life Sciences for developing mobile assisted handheld devices for E.Coli bacteria detection and Arsenic detection</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Collaboration Area: Development of Spectroscopy based E.Coli bacteria detection and Enzyme based Arsenic detection in water</p>\r\n', '<p>1. Technology Transferred to: Manjeera Diamond Towers, A residential community with around 1000 flats for their water management solution</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2. Technology Transferred to: First-Step for Shrimp farm monitoring near Vishakhapatnam</p>\r\n', '<p>1. Solution Provided to: Manjeera Diamond Towers, Hyderabad</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2. Solution Provided to: First-Step, Vishakhapatnam</p>\r\n', '<p>1. Service: Smart Cities Project by SCCE from Teams Up Incubation Center Offered to <strong>Karimnagar Municipal Corporation</strong></p>\r\n', '<p>0</p>\r\n', '<p>1.Consultation under Smart Cities Project by SCCE from Teams Up Incubation Center</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Offered to Karimnagar Municipal Corporation</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2. Consultation under Smart Cities Project by SCIT from Teams Up Incubation Center</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Offered to Karimnagar Municipal Corporation</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3. Consultation offered to NGO Practical Actions</p>\r\n\r\n<p>4. Consultation offered to OXFAM India, Kolkata</p>\r\n', '<p>1. Board: Expert Member, Empowerment Committee on Mobile Governance, MeitY, Govt. of India</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Year: 2015-2017</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2. Board: Member, Advisory Committee, Center of Excellence (Theme: Disaster Management), JNTU, Hyderabad</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Year: 2014-2017</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3. Board: Member, PRSG, Secured Peer-to-Peer Network, DST, Govt. of India</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Year:2014-2016</p>\r\n', 13, '2018-05-22 02:22:43', 'enables', '9');
