(20, 'project438', 5, 'Soumen Basak', 'They did identify the problem that there is a lack of multi-scale, comprehensive model for analysing T2D pathogenesis.  They want to build one and examine in this context amyloidosis in T2D. ', 'One criticism persists that there is a lack of hypothesis with direct relevance to T2D pathogenesis or Amylin biology.  The hypothesis proposed in this study has link to the IT-infrastructure and associated issues. However, given stringently defined deliverables, it is expected the infrastructure will help many others in the biomedical field.', 'It is laudatory that they plan to build a multi-scale software infrastructure for numerical solution of ordinary and stochastic differential equations associated with the amyloidosis molecules and pathways in T2D.\r\nThe model construction will depend on pre-existing literature in T2D, and they have clearly defined the target pathways, and specific goals.  According to this reviewer, two most important specific objectives are coupling of scales and benchmarking with kinetics of Amylin related T2D pathways.', 'NA', 'The objectives are focused are likely to be achieved within three years.  More so, given stringently defined deliverables, it is expected the infrastructure will help many others in the biomedical field.', 'The pre-existing problem of integrating data from various scales (cells, tissue and then organism) has been very nicely articulated. ', 'The project may lack novelty as others have earlier tried to develop multiscale models. But it will be important that a multiscale model exists for T2D.', 'Except for two minor issues as detailed below -\r\n1.  It is important that the investigators develop an web-based interface for their software infrastructure.  It will help researchers in the Biomedical field to use their tools.\r\n2. The investigators elaborately discuss how the training dataset will be generated (literature, other models etc.) for construction of the computational infrastructure.  But it is important that they also discuss how the model outputs will be validated, preferably in a blinded study in association with other biomedical rese', 'The objectives are focused are likely to be achieved within three years.  More so, given stringently defined deliverables, it is expected the infrastructure will help many others in the biomedical field.\r\nIt is important that the investigators also discuss how the model outputs will be validated, preferably in a blinded study in association with biomedical researchers.  It is conceivable that this extended goal is unlikely to be achieved within the stipulated time-line.  But a disclosure to that extent will be important and will assure proper follow', 'Considering many of the participating institutes have active PhD program, manpower budget is somewhat stretched, and should be curtailed.  ', '', '', '', '', 'Travel budget is somewhat inflated, and should be trimmed, particularly international travel should be arranged using alternate funding from other sources.', 'This particular project is likely establish the basic human simulator infrastructure and verify its relevance in T2D.  But the computational infrastructure developed is likely to be then utilised for many other diseases.  It is important that the investigators develop a web interface for facilitating use of their infrastructure by biomedical researcher.  Participation of biomedical researchers will facilitate minor refinement of the model, and improve the model performance.', '', 'YES', 'NO', 'YES', 'NA', 'YES', 'YES', 'NO', 'YES', 'YES', 'NO', 'YES', 'YES', 'YES', 'YES', 'NO', '', 'YES', '', '', '', '0000-00-00'),
(21, 'project453', 6, 'Lipi Thukral', 'The research problem is clearly articulated.', 'The hypothesis is defined towards significance of C-terminal region of alpha-synuclein and its unambiguous role in aggregation propensity. ', 'The proposal aims towards creating a series of C-terminal mutants with emphasis on charged residues. Further, biophysical tools are utilised to distinguish between amyloid and amorphous types of aggregates. Machine learning approaches will be utilised to develop predictive models followed by cytotoxicity studies.', 'NA', 'The feasibility and time deliverables of initial leg of the proposal aims towards site-directed mutagenesis and web-based tool. Later the work converges to model building and prediction. The work is doable because the research scope is limited to specific protein mutants only. It leaves a lot to be desired in terms of other approaches/peptides that could also be included. ', '', '', 'The proposed work includes two aspects, namely, biophysical approaches and predictive models that will primarily define the sequence-specificity towards aggregation. The research project, however, is very targeted and only leverages limited number of approaches. The current scheme requires highly interdiscplinary work-groups to intersect with each other at various interfaces. ', 'The feasibility is highly likely due to narrow targets.', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'The proposed project is utilising biophysical approaches and machine learning tools to gather insights about C-terminal mutants of alpha-synuclein. The work proposed is very narrow in its approach and therefore not suitable for a large-interdisciplinary range.', 'YES', 'YES', 'YES', 'NA', 'YES', 'YES', 'NO', 'YES', 'YES', 'NO', 'NO', 'NO', 'NO', 'NO', 'NO', '', 'NO', '', '', '', '0000-00-00'),
(22, 'project427', 6, 'Lipi Thukral', 'The research proposal has a very wide scope of investigations and therefore the exact problem to be addressed is missing. ', 'The hypothesis behind the proposed work is the unmet need of neurological biomarker to predict disease progression', 'The objectives of the proposal are general and not specific. e.g., Pg 4 highlights technical overview of the objectives which are not precise and do not explain exact deliverables. ', 'NA', 'The project aims towards covering clinico-biological tests, biophysical, biochemical and genetic markers for prognosis of AD. This is followed by model construction with feature extraction, and development of webpage. The feasibility of all the objectives in a given 3 years time is hence not possible. The project is therefore not targeted and loses focus. ', '', '', 'The proposal does not reflect the idea of integrated biological approaches that are interdisciplinary in nature. The project is therefore aiming to touch a lot of topics but does not integrate them coherently for studying the development and progression of the disease. ', 'Not feasible.', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'The project is too vague and objectives are covering breadth of topics to study early stages of AD. Additionally, the proposed work does not utilise integrative approaches with clear deliverables. ', 'NO', 'NO', 'NO', 'NA', 'NO', 'NO', 'NO', 'NO', 'NO', 'NO', 'NO', 'NO', 'NO', 'NO', 'NO', '', 'NO', '', '', '', '0000-00-00'),
(23, 'project428', 6, 'Lipi Thukral', 'The research problem is clearly articulated.', 'Yes, the hypothesis underlying research proposal is the lack of available robust computational model to predict AD disease development and progression. In particular, whole brain models that can infer large range of pathophysiological processes from neuroimaging data.', 'The key objectives of the project include construction of a computational model that would predict from various patients datasets (such as fMRI, and cognitive tests), the disease progession. ', 'NA', 'The timelines and deliverables of each objectives are very sound and doable. ', '', '', 'The scope of work of the highly interdisciplinary in nature. The proposed work includes complementary techniques that are addressing challenges at different scales, such as: at macroscale they plan to identify factors that are contributing to inhibitory mechanisms. At cellular and metabolism scale they aim to investigate unknown entities in the UPR pathway and their manifestations. Lastly, molecular dynamics simulations will reveal protein-scale information on putative targets.', 'Overall project is feasible except certain parts of Objective 4 that includes MD simulations that are too exploratory in nature. Exact nature of protein systems to be studied will be the outcome of previous experiments and hence nothing can be commented yet.', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'The project is well-knit and integrative in nature. It draws upon variety of distinct and complementary approaches to built a robust computational model.', 'YES', 'YES', 'YES', 'NA', 'YES', 'YES', 'YES', 'YES', 'YES', 'NO', 'YES', 'YES', 'YES', 'YES', 'NO', '', 'YES', '', '', '', '0000-00-00'),
